#ident	"@(#)devintf:groups/mbrship/add/Help	1.2"

add:ABSTRACT:
	The "add" task adds a device to the membership of a device group.  You
	will be asked to supply the name of the device group and the name of a
	device to add to the membership of that group.

Form.add:Name:the Group Name field
	This field names the device group to which you wish to add a member.
	
	The device group must be a valid group name (i.e. containing only
	alphanumeric characters, '.', '-', '_', and '$', and no longer than
	14 characters.  This field may not be blank.

Form.add:Member:the Group Member field
	This field names the device alias that is to be added to the named
	device group.  If the alias is specified that is not currently defined,
	the task will issue a warning message but accept the alias as a member.
	
	The aliases must be valid aliases (i.e. they contain only alphanumeric
	characters and the characters '.', '-', '_', and '$' and contain no
	more than 14 characters.  These fields may not be blank.
